{"tid":1310513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「必聽」為何林鄭不能說撤回","createTime":"2019-07-12T16:49:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T06:03:15.000Z","uid":20689,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f7c4df55c420d3d11bc015dd356ae1546b7dde8e","tid":1310513,"uid":20689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:49:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tuWnPgYelXs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtuWnPgYelXs&d=f11PFKDsvG%2B7MRfNo%2B80BW7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=84d943c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tuWnPgYelXs</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重點：<br />\n1. 香港真正話事人係中共，港共 林鄭只係偽政權<br />\n2. 中共仲未能夠定性香港事件點處理 需要更多時間決定<br />\n3. 一國兩制已經完結 特區政府不能控制香港"},{"pid":"9bd0c686047dffe993b84a03ef622a6abeb12103","tid":1310513,"uid":38364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:50:04.000Z","msg":"[快撚啲同我入黎推撚爆佢] 民陣721金鐘集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1307890\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1307890</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"509e7881e0289b28bf87f4abec11fbfedecf87d9","tid":1310513,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:50:40.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借個位<br />\n<br />\n[五毛分化警示] 散佈失敗論，叫人聚焦，放棄其他野，去金鐘，乃一貫分化技倆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1306283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1306283</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔守唔硬碰冇問題，但我唔撚明點解有人借機帶風向，話唔好再搞連儂牆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304714\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304714</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n今日突然多左好多風向話區區遊行無用，連儂牆無用，其實咁先代表佢地仲係好有用，大家唔好中計<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304865\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304865</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n對連儂牆既一啲諗法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304579\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304579</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［置頂，極緊要，極長文］唔好再話連儂牆無用也也也，連儂牆甚至可能係呢一場運動既致勝關鍵！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1301800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1301800</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n共產黨其實怕我地搞地區工作多過出金鐘<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304935\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304935</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2f723973790e7b9cdb0c8b213e90264f28689500","tid":1310513,"uid":26506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:50:56.000Z","msg":"She's well paid for it"},{"pid":"22142a363d44c26c2df7397e563600c91a660b03","tid":1310513,"uid":52621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T17:18:02.000Z","msg":"4. 要保被捕義士就要KEEP住運動熱度"},{"pid":"1960548c4d14081d23198c263ee2a91cc6375f48","tid":1310513,"uid":52621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T17:22:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fed432b4ea80c17dc3b745880e38edd2bddc1821","tid":1310513,"uid":52621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T17:35:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c619a210a39c6b89b6db2d0503baf1e29c83aa1","tid":1310513,"uid":39842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T17:38:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b78a9015e39547ef792837b249fadd8a1fc9f76","tid":1310513,"uid":238013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T17:42:35.000Z","msg":"簡單啦，林奠切腹囉"},{"pid":"2f11151ac86830f8f9e035f0a84c5aee64079860","tid":1310513,"uid":20689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T00:22:47.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"740cf967be44a7d8c5b6c0bfd59504a9247d5cf5","tid":1310513,"uid":52621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T03:34:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d4c79fc2b289d3a098975d07b2bb5bd08f15d71","tid":1310513,"uid":54535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep